- **USA and China highlighted** in Economist Blue (`#1A476F`); the remaining three economies are muted (`#B8C4CE`) to draw focus to the gap
- **Red bracket annotation** (`#C74634`) marks the $7.5T gap between the two leaders
- **Y-axis starts at zero**, no truncation
- **No chartjunk** — no 3D, no shadows, no right/top spines, subtle dashed gridlines
